title: Free Star Guardian Logo
body: Hi, i recently did the the which star guardian are you quiz and have not yet received my summoner icon. Its been over a week and i really don't wanna miss out on this limited time only icon as I'm a huge fan of the star guardian range. :/

replies.body:
Hey there all,

I'm unsure of the exact distribution period for these icons, but i'd give it a little bit longer (5 days) and if you've still not received anything then feel free to [submit a ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/requests/new) to Player Support regarding the issue.
same problem, i did the quiz on my 2 accounts, still haven't received the icon. it's been 4 days.
